title: HATCHETMEN - Judge & Jury (2011)
description:
First effort from Detroit power trio HATCHETMEN. Original blues rock. Think Neil Young fronting Gov't Mule. Dick Lonczynski (yours truly...) - Guitars & Vocals. Randy Dunn - Drums. Reg Nicholas - Bass guitar. Recorded by "Motor City" Josh Ford. Mixed, mastered & produced by Peter Jay. All titles written and arranged by Dick Lonczynski.

01 Lucky Stiff
02 What About Me?
03 I Ain't Sayin'
04 What Are You Waiting For?
05 Ain't As Old (As I Used To Be)
06 Tell The Truth
07 Omar Comin'!
08 Marvin
09 Headin' Up North
10 Trashman
11 Cookie Crumbles

320kkps CBR
